  "westernTraditionalUsage": {
    "en": "Borage, also known as starflower, is grown across Europe, north Africa and Iran. It is used as a diuretic, a demulcent and emollient as well as being prized for its culinary uses. Borage is also sometimes used to alleviate and heal colds, bronchitis, and respiratory infections because of its anti-inflammatory and balsamic properties. In France it is used to treat fevers and pulmonary complaints. Externally, it is useful as a poultice for inflammatory swellings.\n",
    "zh-Hant": "琉璃苣可當作小便暢通劑、止痛劑和潤膚劑。在法國, 琉璃苣經常被用作治療發燒和肺病。外塗方面, 琉璃苣濕敷於膨脹的發炎傷口上。\n",
    "zh-Hans": "琉璃苣可当作小便畅通剂、止痛剂和润肤剂。在法国, 琉璃苣经常被用作治疗发烧和肺病。外塗方面, 琉璃苣湿敷於膨胀的发炎伤口上。\n"
  },
